item.title: How to hide ur client files so u can release it
item.dc:creator: @noob_pwner noob pwner
item.description:
@noob_pwner wrote:

its easy, just make a copy of it on your desktop and then open it, compile one last time, delete all java files and the compiler, then put it into a .rar and upload. that way, no one can edit your client unless they had a decompiler.
